---
const M = '/assets/media/projects/web-dev/bellelachaise';
---

<section class="blcw-project relative container mx-auto flex flex-col gap-4 px-4 py-4">
  <div class="project-summary-card blcw-card">
    <div class="blcw-card-inner flex flex-col gap-4">
      <h1 class="font-display m-0 text-4xl uppercase">Bellelachaise</h1>

      <div class="blcw-copy">
        <p>
          Bellelachaise, under the passionate guidance of founder Hakim, is a minimalist trilingual
          e-commerce platform that brings carefully curated vintage furniture to life through a serene
          Japandi-inspired design. I conceived and built the site using Shopify, crafting an intuitive
          shopping journey with secure checkout, seamless inventory management and SEO-optimized
          performance. The site is fully trilingual, offering content in English, French and Dutch to
          reach a broader audience. The result is a refined digital boutique where every piece tells
          its own story and browsing feels effortlessly elegant.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between">
        <div class="md:w-8/12">
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl tracking-wide uppercase">Responsibilities</h2>
          <p class="blcw-copy">
            Web design personalization, Shopify setup, site development and features personalization,
            website launch, client training on back-office management.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-4/12 md:pl-10">
          <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl tracking-wide uppercase">URL</h2>
          <a href="https://bellelachaise.be/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="blcw-copy text-inherit">
            bellelachaise.be
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="gallery-grid">
    <div class="grid-row row1">
      <div class="grid-item landscape"><img src={`${M}/blc-desktop-image1-960.avif`} alt="Bellelachaise desktop 1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
      <div class="grid-item landscape"><img src={`${M}/blc-desktop-image2-960.avif`} alt="Bellelachaise desktop 2" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-row row2">
      <div class="grid-item stack">
        <div class="stack-item"><img src={`${M}/blc-desktop-image5-960.avif`} alt="Bellelachaise desktop 3" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
        <div class="stack-item"><img src={`${M}/blc-desktop-image4-960.avif`} alt="Bellelachaise desktop 4" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-item portrait"><img src={`${M}/blc-mobile-image1-960.avif`} alt="Bellelachaise mobile 1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
      <div class="grid-item portrait"><img src={`${M}/blc-mobile-image2-960.avif`} alt="Bellelachaise mobile 2" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-row row3">
      <div class="grid-item portrait"><img src={`${M}/blc-mobile-image3-960.avif`} alt="Bellelachaise mobile 3" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
      <div class="grid-item stack landscape-stack">
        <div class="stack-item"><img src={`${M}/blc-desktop-image6-960.avif`} alt="Bellelachaise desktop 5" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
        <div class="stack-item"><img src={`${M}/blc-desktop-image3-960.avif`} alt="Bellelachaise desktop 6" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-item portrait"><img src={`${M}/blc-mobile-image4-960.avif`} alt="Bellelachaise mobile 4" loading="lazy" decoding="async" /></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .blcw-card {
    border-radius: var(--project-card-radius);
  }
  .blcw-card-inner {
    padding: 1rem;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .blcw-card-inner {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
  .blcw-card h2 {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  .blcw-copy {
    font-family: 'Red Hat Text', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
</style>
